title: Channels of the reaction Li-7(gamma,p)He-6.

x4freetext: Channels of the reaction Li-7(gamma,p)He-6.

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Yadernaya Fizika, Vol.20, Issue.6, p.1106 (1974)
Jour: Soviet Journal of Nuclear Physics, Vol.20, p.579 (1975)

x4freetext: Energy distributions of photoprotons from Li-7 at 40
values of the bremsstrahlung end-point energy were
measured with the step delta(Eg-max)=1 MeV up from
Eg-max=15.5 MeV. Analysis of these distributions
established that the final nucleus He-6 may Be produced
with excitation energies up to=17 MeV. Besides the
detected transitions to the ground state and to the
first excited state (1.8 MeV) of the nucleus He-6,there
are some indications to that the transitions proceed
also to levels (or groups of the levels) with energies
2.5 and 8.5 MeV,unknown previously. The partial cross
sections of the reaction (g,p) with production of He-6
are obtained by means of the isochromate method.
Statistical errors only.
Data from Fig. 3.
Corrected by V.Varlamov, V.Mclane
